author: julianfoad
msg: On the 'move-tracking-2' branch: Slightly change the metadata storage
format, and no longer parse the root path of a branch from it. Leave that
information in the metadata in the form of a comment for us humans.
The reason is that the root path is not an essential attribute of the branch.
* subversion/libsvn_delta/branch.c
(svn_branch_get_default_r0_metadata): Adjust accordingly.
(parse_branch_line): No longer parse and return the root path.
(svn_branch_state_parse): No longer receive (and ignore) the root path.
(svn_branch_state_serialize): Write the root path in a slightly different
form, like a comment, and using absolute path notation.
* subversion/tests/cmdline/svntest/wc.py
(_re_parse_eid_branch,
State.from_eids): Adjust accordingly.

author: rhuijben
msg: * generator/templates/vcnet_vcxproj.ezt
Pass resource compiler include directories and defines globally instead of
per .rc file. This makes the generated file more closely match that of
a normal user created project file.
